{"tid":2338487,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"Nowhere Boys出新歌俾下一代 《種子》","createTime":"2020-12-24T04:56:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-16T01:33:30.000Z","uid":376027,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"19b1181ad5580347717476fd6c73d7477cf0ba72","tid":2338487,"uid":376027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T04:56:27.000Z","msg":"所有事物到了最後並不代表完結，而是一個新的開始。在2020的冬至，我們把今年最後的一首歌《種子》送給你們，希望能帶來一點暖意。<br />\n致我們的下一代：要茁壯地成長🌱<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GJE35kxhknE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGJE35kxhknE&d=otIFGLHjmDp%2FicXUVK76MdjJpSEh9fPrneULq4V%2BA60%3D&h=6fd85893\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GJE35kxhknE</a><br />\n<br />\nNowhere Boys - 種子<br />\n<br />\n作詞：Fisher Kan<br />\n作曲：Fisher Kan<br />\n編曲：Nowhere Boys<br />\n監製：謝國維<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"teal\"><strong>一寸寸地邁向更高天空 為了那初衷<br />\n一次次地墮進各種困局 要怎麼繼續<br />\n<br />\n能茁壯成長的精彩 難免比幻想更可愛<br />\n<strong><span class=\"large\"><span class=\"gold\">奉獻了你我這一代 無須到老才慷慨<br />\n留到某日看着花海 無非悉心灌溉</span></span></strong><br />\n難過 仍要 期待<br />\n<br />\n無須擔心無聲的未來</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n叫大家要撐住，唔好唔記得班後生仔呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />明明上年組合銀，又黃到金都得果1355views<br />\n<br />\n之前仲出過小丑，諷刺香港已經顛覆曬，要比個世界更癲先生存到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7856730f86eb30e4fca743ff296112e140e6e3c","tid":2338487,"uid":376027,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T05:05:25.000Z","msg":"呢首歌係上年已經有拎上 風雨中抱緊你，但係今年演唱會先正式release<br />\n果版嘅歌詞仲出面，仲更加直白<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/my903/videos/2357026591249528/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fm